NIGHTWATCH OVERRIDE — AUTHORISATION
----------------------------------------

At 22:00 UTC on 2026-01-18 I initiated
the standard duty officer override to
suppress NIGHTWATCH real-time alerting
for the 22:00–00:00 window.

This is a routine procedure used during
scheduled maintenance windows to prevent
false positive alert cascades from
reaching the IR on-call roster.

Override authorisation code : DO-OVR-18JAN-004
Override duration           : 22:00 UTC to 00:00 UTC
Reason logged               : Sub-level 2 routine maintenance window

I confirm that at the time of initiating
the override I was not aware of any
active threat or anomalous behaviour in
Sub-level 2.

